{"tid":1936412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"721事件8個月　元朗站部份出口下午4時關閉","createTime":"2020-03-21T08:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T08:14:57.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"90ea9636ef585f13fb50165ddffa92e758286994","tid":1936412,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"721事件8個月 元朗站部份出口下午4時關閉<br />\n<br />\n元朗721暴力襲擊事件發生8個月，有市民在網上發起到元朗遊行或在不同港鐵站靜坐等活動，港鐵未有提早關閉元朗站，指元朗站現時維持運作，但A、B、J、K及H出口下午4時起暫時關閉，以管理車站人流，呼籲乘客使用其他出入口進出車站及留意職員指示。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275451&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1275451%26csid%3D261_341&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92Fwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=9920a960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275451&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}